       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI58406.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI58406.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Emissăo Plano Facturaçăo                                   *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI58406         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5008 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0104 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV5840.
       COPY COCV5841.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ATCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY ETCK0001.
       COPY ETCK0002.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.
       COPY AQCW0009.
       COPY ARCL2720.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COB04100             PIC X(08) VALUE 'COB04100'.
           05 CON-COB04200             PIC X(08) VALUE 'COB04200'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO     PIC X(08).

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI58406'.

       01  WS-COB04100-DATA.
           10 COB04100-NIDPROJECTO PIC X(08)  VALUE SPACES.
           10 COB04100-CTO         PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI58406         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV5840-MSG.
           MOVE COCV5840-ASE               TO COCV5841-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5840-ADE               TO COCV5841-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-CRIA-DADOS
                 THRU 2200-CRIA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2450-OBT-EMAIL
                 THRU 2450-OBT-EMAIL-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-ENVIA-EMAIL
                 THRU 2500-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-CRIA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-CRIA-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-CRIA-DADOS    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5840-NIDPROJECTO TO COB04100-NIDPROJECTO.

           CALL CON-COB04100    USING AQCW0009-DATA
                                      WS-COB04100-DATA
           END-CALL.

       2200-CRIA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2500-ENVIA-EMAIL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-ENVIA-EMAIL.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-ENVIA-EMAIL' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           CALL CON-COB04200    USING AQCW0009-DATA
                                      WS-COB04100-DATA
           END-CALL.

       2500-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   OBTEM EMAIL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2450-OBT-EMAIL.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2450-OBT-EMAIL      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE  SPACES               TO COB04100-CTO.
           MOVE  VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I  TO ARCD0104-GUSERNAME.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GEMAIL
                  INTO :ARCD0104-GEMAIL
                  FROM  ARVT0104
                 WHERE  GUSERNAME  = :ARCD0104-GUSERNAME
           END-EXEC.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
                MOVE ARCD0104-GEMAIL TO COB04100-CTO
             ELSE
                MOVE 'Utilizador năo tem email'
                                             TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'ARCD0104-GUSERNAME  '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE ARCD0104-GUSERNAME      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                  THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2450-OBT-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV5841-NIDPROJECTO   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV5841-NIDPROJECTO     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV5841-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV5841-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV5841-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY AQCP0005.
           COPY ARCP2720.
